Poll: Fire 50% of managers at random. Does your company survive?
text:
Consider the org chart at your current company.

For this poll, a manager is somebody with 2 or more subordinates.

Fire each manager by coin-flip.

Could your org survive this arrangement without hiring for 1 year?

[1] https://taylor.town/thanos-management
